{"id":232828892,"title":"存股活化資產的小確幸","content":"一直有在關注所謂的借券，但之前借券信託對我們小資來說門檻實在有點高。\n直到去年4月，我開始用雙向借券，一張也能出借！真的是另外的小確幸，累積到現在大概賺了3-4000塊。\n雖然不多但是積沙成塔，在邊累積存股時，邊有另外的現金流進來也是一種鼓勵（股利）啊！\n對了，記得也要比較不同帳戶的利息喔！\n每個月1號我都會去把證券交割戶（年息0.01%）裡面的借券息轉帳到我的薪轉戶（光活存也有0.27%，只有搭車時間動動手指頭利息就差27倍了！（我的網銀有提供每個月幾次的轉帳免手續費）。\n最重要的是有了知識以後，執行力才能讓夢想逐步轉變為現實。\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1122bb89-316f-472f-aa80-fe1fcbe28d1a/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/c93a39e6-2e96-439b-a209-c1250063d637/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"一直有在關注所謂的借券，但之前借券信託對我們小資來說門檻實在有點高。直到去年4月，我開始用雙向借券，一張也能出借！真的是另外的小確幸，累積到現在大概賺了3-4000塊。雖然不多但是積沙成塔，在邊累積存","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"3bceb81c-574e-4a96-8050-4df56096d0df","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-05T06:29:05.138Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-05T06:29:05.138Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["理財"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"理財","forumAlias":"money","school":"中華民國陸軍軍官學校","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1122bb89-316f-472f-aa80-fe1fcbe28d1a/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/c93a39e6-2e96-439b-a209-c1250063d637/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f0388d0e-537e-4329-83c7-b87df6d0dfc0","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1122bb89-316f-472f-aa80-fe1fcbe28d1a/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1122bb89-316f-472f-aa80-fe1fcbe28d1a/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1122bb89-316f-472f-aa80-fe1fcbe28d1a/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-05T06:29:05.138Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-05T06:29:05.138Z","width":296,"hei